Name: elaine
About the game: This is elaine! A minimalistic tile-matching action game by Slight Super Powers. Frantically guiding your player tile around a sensile platform to match the incoming pattern in time. In this deceptively simple game, you'll have to deal with a shifting screen, multi-colored patterns of increasing speed and complexity, and an unrelenting countdown timer synced to brain-pumping music. Features: six uniquely challenging levels highly addictive gameplay pulsing electronic soundtrack minimalistic game design obsessive global leaderboards accurate pantone color reproduction non-stop action
